t. When you enter your home, pray two cycles to prevent you from an evil entrance.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Bazza\u0304r 8567 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34519,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/25\/jibreel-teaches-prophet-refuge\/","url_meta":{"origin":23351,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Refuge: Gabriel teaches the Prophet to seek refuge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Khanbash reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGabriel came to me and he said: O Muhammad, speak! I said: What should I say? Gabriel said: Say, I seek refuge in the perfect words of Allah from the evil of what He\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34715,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/21\/prophet-teaches-refuge\/","url_meta":{"origin":23351,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet teaches a man to seek refuge in Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Shakal ibn Humayd reported: I came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, teach me to seek refuge that by it I may seek refuge.\u201d The Prophet took me by the hand and he said, \u201cSay: O Allah, I seek refuge\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u06